    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for affordable wheels without the big price tag? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport or a solid little project. It\u2019s got the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect, but there\u2019s still plenty of value here for the right buyer. If you want something cheap, practical, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
