    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Great opportunity for someone who knows their way around a wrench. This car is in poor cosmetic and overall condition, but it still offers a strong platform with proven mechanical fundamentals and plenty of usable life for the right buyer. The engine pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels capable, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable setup that makes it appealing as a budget commuter, project, or parts donor. Expect wear, blemishes, and needed attention, but for someone looking for an affordable entry point, there is real value here.",
